                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "The ENCAP Reconstitution Program involves collective, cooperative NAVAIR and NAVSEA effort to re-integrate ENCAP AURs and capability back into USN LA-class nuclear-powered attack submarines.  Navy efforts within NAVSEA and NAVAIR include the refurbishment, preparation, and test firing of several Encapsulated Harpoon Certification and Training Vehicles (EHCVTs) at-sea from several LA-class SSNs as well as shock and implosion safety studies and analysis with supporting tests, reports, and engineering documents."
